trans-unit.source: Provides a cursor model for navigating and editing XML data.
trans-unit.target: 为定位和编辑 XML 数据提供游标模型。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> class in the <xref:System.Xml.XPath?displayProperty=nameWithType> namespace is an abstract class which defines a cursor model for navigating and editing XML information items as instances of the XQuery 1.0 and XPath 2.0 Data Model.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>类<xref:System.Xml.XPath?displayProperty=nameWithType>命名空间是一个抽象类，它定义用于导航和编辑为 XQuery 1.0 和 XPath 2.0 数据模型的实例的 XML 信息项的游标模型。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object is created from a class that implements the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable> interface such as the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument> and <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> classes.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>对象创建一个类以实现从<xref:System.Xml.XPath.IXPathNavigable>如<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument>和<xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>类。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> objects created by <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument> objects are read-only while <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> objects created by <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> objects can be edited.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> 创建的对象<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathDocument>对象为只读时<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>创建的对象<xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>对象可以进行编辑。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object's read-only or editable status is determined using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CanEdit%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>使用确定对象的只读或可编辑状态<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CanEdit%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>类。

trans-unit.source: For more information about processing XML data using the XPath data model, see the [Process XML Data Using the XPath Data Model](~/docs/standard/data/xml/process-xml-data-using-the-xpath-data-model.md) topic.
trans-unit.target: 有关处理使用 XPath 数据模型的 XML 数据的详细信息，请参阅[使用 XPath 数据模型处理 XML 数据](~/docs/standard/data/xml/process-xml-data-using-the-xpath-data-model.md)主题。

trans-unit.source: Exceptions raised as a result of using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> class, such as the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathException> class, may contain sensitive information that should not be exposed in untrusted scenarios.
trans-unit.target: 由于使用而引发的异常<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>类，如<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathException>类中，可能包含不应在不受信任的方案中公开的敏感信息。

trans-unit.source: Exceptions should be properly handled so that this sensitive information is not exposed in untrusted scenarios.
trans-unit.target: 应正确处理异常，以便在不受信任的情况下不公开此敏感信息。

trans-unit.source: Appending child nodes adds the new nodes to the end of the list of child nodes for the current node.

trans-unit.source: For example, when three child nodes exist for an element, the first appended node becomes the fourth child node.

trans-unit.source: If no child nodes exist, then a new child node is created.
trans-unit.target: 如果不存在任何子节点，然后创建新的子节点。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventHandler" /> that receives information about schema validation warnings and errors.
trans-unit.target: 接收有关架构验证警告和错误消息的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventHandler" />。

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the XML data in the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> conforms to the XML Schema definition language (XSD) schema provided.
trans-unit.target: 验证 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 中的 XML 数据是否符合所提供的 XML 架构定义语言 (XSD) 架构。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if no schema validation errors occurred; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果未出现架构验证错误，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CheckValidity%2A> method verifies that the XML data contained in the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> conforms to a global type or declaration in the schema or schemas provided in the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CheckValidity%2A>方法验证 XML 数据中包含<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>符合全局类型或声明中或多个架构中提供<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CheckValidity%2A> method does not perform infoset augmentation.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CheckValidity%2A>方法不执行信息集增加。

trans-unit.source: This means that schema defaults are not applied, text values are not converted to atomic values, and no new type information is associated with information items.
trans-unit.target: 这意味着，架构的默认值不会应用中，文本值不会转换为原子值，而不与信息项关联的任何新的类型信息。

trans-unit.source: Schema `xsi:schemaLocation` or `xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation` hints in the XML data of are ignored.
trans-unit.target: 架构`xsi:schemaLocation`或`xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation`的 XML 数据中的提示将被忽略。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on a document node, the validation process includes checking of uniqueness and reference constraints (`xs:ID`, `xs:IDREF`, `xs:key`, `xs:keyref`, and `xs:unique`).
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>定位在文档节点上，则验证过程包括唯一性和引用约束的检查 (`xs:ID`， `xs:IDREF`， `xs:key`， `xs:keyref`，和`xs:unique`)。

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, these checks are omitted.
trans-unit.target: 否则，将忽略这些检查。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> passed as a parameter is `null` and the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on an element node, the type information exposed by the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property's <xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A> property is used to check the node's validity.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>参数原样传递`null`和<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>定位在元素节点上，通过公开的类型信息<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>属性的<xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A>属性用于检查节点的有效性。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> passed as a parameter is `null` and the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on the root node, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property of the document element (that is, the element child of the root node) is used.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>参数原样传递`null`和<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>位于根节点中，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>使用的文档元素 （即，子元素的根节点） 属性。

trans-unit.source: In both cases if the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A> property of the element's <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property is `null` and the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet> passed as a parameter is `null`, an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> is thrown because there is no type information to use to perform validation.
trans-unit.target: 在这两种情况下如果<xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A>元素的属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>属性是`null`和<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet>参数原样传递`null`、<xref:System.InvalidOperationException>之所以引发因为用于执行无类型信息验证。

trans-unit.source: A schema validation error occurred, and no <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventHandler" /> was specified to handle validation errors.
trans-unit.target: 出现架构验证错误，并且未指定任何 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventHandler" /> 处理验证错误。

trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 定位在不是元素、特性或根节点的节点上，或者不存在用于执行验证的类型信息。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CheckValidity(System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet,System.Xml.Schema.ValidationEventHandler)" /> method was called with an <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaSet" /> parameter when the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> was not positioned on the root node of the XML data.

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, creates a new <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> positioned at the same node as this <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" />.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中被重写时，创建一个新的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" />，它定位到的节点与此 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 定位到的节点相同。

trans-unit.source: A new <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> positioned at the same node as this <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个新的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" />，它定位到的节点与此 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 定位到的节点相同。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Clone%2A> method is especially useful in conjunction with the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Clone%2A>方法是特别有用结合<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>。

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator> is used to iterate over a selected node set, and contains a <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator.Current%2A> property which returns an <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> positioned on the context node of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>可用于循环访问所选的节点集，并包含<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator.Current%2A>属性返回<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>定位在的上下文节点上<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator>。

trans-unit.source: However, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> returned by the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator.Current%2A> property cannot be used to move away from the node set.
trans-unit.target: 但是，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>返回<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeIterator.Current%2A>属性不能用于将移开节点集。

trans-unit.source: Instead, you clone the returned <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> and use the cloned navigator to do any additional moves.
trans-unit.target: 相反，您应该克隆返回<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>并使用克隆导航器执行任何附加移动。

trans-unit.source: The cloned <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is not affected by subsequent changes to the original <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 克隆<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>与原始的后续更改的情况下不会影响<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: When comparing nodes in the XML document, the following rules apply:
trans-unit.target: 如果将 XML 文档中的节点进行比较，以下规则适用：

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Element> nodes: These nodes are returned in document order from the source document.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Element> 节点： 从源文档按文档顺序返回这些节点。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Namespace> nodes: These nodes may be returned in document order and are always before the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Attribute> nodes of the parent element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Namespace> 节点： 这些节点可能按文档顺序返回，始终前<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Attribute>节点的父元素。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Attribute> nodes: These nodes may be returned in document order.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Attribute> 节点： 可能按文档顺序返回这些节点。

trans-unit.source: They always come after the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Namespace> nodes and before any child nodes of the parent node.
trans-unit.target: 它们总是后<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNodeType.Namespace>节点和任何子节点的父节点之前。

trans-unit.source: An XPath expression is evaluated to yield one of the following return types:
trans-unit.target: XPath 表达式进行计算以产生下列返回类型之一：

trans-unit.source: Node Set: an unordered collection of nodes without duplicates
trans-unit.target: 节点集： 一个无序的集合的无重复节点

trans-unit.source: Boolean: `true` or `false`
trans-unit.target: 布尔值：`true`或 `false`

trans-unit.source: Number: a floating-point number
trans-unit.target: 浮点数的数目：

trans-unit.source: String: a sequence of UCS characters
trans-unit.target: 字符串： UCS 字符序列

trans-unit.source: Expressions that return a node set can be used in the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Select%2A> and <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Evaluate%2A> methods.

trans-unit.source: For example to create a new attribute on an element in the default namespace of the `contosoBooks.xml` file, (`xmlns="http://www.contoso.com/books"`), you specify `null` or <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=nameWithType> for both the namespace prefix and namespace URI parameters.

trans-unit.source: Specifying `http://www.contoso.com/books` as the namespace URI parameter will cause the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.CreateAttribute%2A> method to auto generate a namespace prefix for the new attribute.

trans-unit.source: If the new attribute created is a namespace node which conflicts with a namespace declaration on the element, either because the namespace prefix chosen is used by another namespace declaration at the same scope, or because the prefix chosen is the same as that of the element but is bound to a different namespace URI, an exception is thrown.

trans-unit.target: 多个引用相同的命名空间的前缀以任何特定的方式，因此特定前缀可能不会返回多个分配时每次，URI 才不进行排序。

trans-unit.source: Namespace URI to prefix mappings can change from node to node in an XML document.
trans-unit.target: Namespace URI 的前缀映射可以更改 XML 文档中的从一个节点到另一个节点。

trans-unit.source: As a result, the value of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupPrefix%2A> method may not be consistent from one node to the next.
trans-unit.target: 因此的值<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupPrefix%2A>方法可能会不一致从一个节点到下一步。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> object positioned on the element boundary which the current <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> will not move past while searching for the following element.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 对象，该对象定位在搜索下一个元素时当前 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 不会越过的元素边界上。

trans-unit.source: Moves the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> to the element with the local name and namespace URI specified, to the boundary specified, in document order.
trans-unit.target: 按文档顺序将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移动到指定的边界内具有指定的本地名称和命名空间 URI 的元素。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> moved successfully; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移动成功，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> boundary passed as a parameter is not positioned after the position of the current <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> it is ignored.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>作为参数传递的边界未定位在当前的位置后<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>它将被忽略。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> boundary parameter is `null`, the following element with the local name and namespace URI specified is located in document order.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>边界参数是`null`，按文档顺序查找具有的本地名称和命名空间 URI 的以下元素。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A> methods cannot be used to move to attribute or namespace nodes.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A>方法无法用于将移动到属性或命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> boundary passed as a parameter is positioned over an attribute or namespace node, it is equivalent to the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> boundary parameter having been positioned on the first child node of its parent element.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>作为一个参数是否位于某个属性或命名空间节点传递的边界，则相当于<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>边界参数具有定位在其父元素的第一个子节点上。

trans-unit.source: This ensures that the parent element of the attribute or namespace node that the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> boundary parameter is positioned on can be matched by this method.
trans-unit.target: 这样可确保属性或命名空间节点的父元素的<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>边界参数位于在可以通过此方法匹配。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A> method returns `false`, the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A>方法返回`false`的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>保持不变。

trans-unit.source: In the following example, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is moved from the root of the `contosoBooks.xml` file to the following `book` element.
trans-unit.target: 在下面的示例中，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>根中移动`contosoBooks.xml`文件复制到以下`book`元素。

trans-unit.source: A clone of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object is made using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Clone%2A> method and is moved from the `book` element to the following `first-name` element.
trans-unit.target: 克隆<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>对象进行身份验证使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Clone%2A>方法，并且移动中`book`元素与以下`first-name`元素。

trans-unit.source: The cloned <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>, positioned on the `first-name` element, will be used as a boundary.
trans-unit.target: 克隆<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>，它定位在`first-name`元素，将用作为边界。

trans-unit.source: Changes in the position of the cloned <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> do not affect the original <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 克隆的位置中的更改<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>不会影响原始<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: The original <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> then attempts to move to the following `price` element using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A> method with the boundary passed as a parameter.
trans-unit.target: 原始<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>然后尝试将移到以下`price`元素使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFollowing%2A>与边界的方法作为参数传递。

trans-unit.source: This move fails because the following `price` element is beyond the boundary.
trans-unit.target: 此移动失败，因为以下`price`元素不在边界。

trans-unit.source: The original <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> then attempts to move to the following `title` element which is before the boundary using the same method and succeeds.
trans-unit.target: 原始<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>然后尝试将移到以下`title`元素它之前使用相同的方法的边界和成功之处。

trans-unit.source: The example takes the `contosoBooks.xml` file as an input.
trans-unit.target: 该示例使用 `contosoBooks.xml` 文件作为输入。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> representing the <c>ID</c> value of the node to which you want to move.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.String" />，表示要移动到的节点的 <c>ID</c> 值。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in a derived class, moves to the node that has an attribute of type <c>ID</c> whose value matches the specified <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: 当在派生类中重写时，移动到具有 <c>ID</c> 类型的属性并且属性值与指定的 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 匹配的节点。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is successful moving; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 成功移动，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="false" />, the position of the navigator is unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果为 <see langword="false" />，则导航器的位置未更改。

trans-unit.source: This method can be used to identify nodes by unique `ID` provided the source document explicitly declares attributes of type `ID` using a DTD.
trans-unit.target: 此方法可以用于标识节点由唯一`ID`提供源文档中显式声明类型的属性`ID`使用 DTD。

trans-unit.source: For example, suppose the following XML data, `<data><x a="a1"/></data>`, was loaded using a DTD that included the following: `<!ATTLIST x a ID #REQUIRED>`.
trans-unit.target: 例如，假设下面的 XML 数据， `<data><x a="a1"/></data>`，使用包含以下 DTD 加载： `<!ATTLIST x a ID #REQUIRED>`。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> was positioned somewhere in the XML data, calling `MoveToId("a1")` positions the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> on the element node `x`.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>所调用的 XML 数据中某个位置处`MoveToId("a1")`位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>元素节点上`x`。

trans-unit.source: The namespace prefix of the namespace node.
trans-unit.target: 命名空间节点的命名空间前缀。

trans-unit.source: Moves the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> to the namespace node with the specified namespace prefix.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移动到具有指定的命名空间前缀的命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is successful moving to the specified namespace; <see langword="false" /> if a matching namespace node was not found, or if the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is not positioned on an element node.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 成功移动到指定的命名空间，则为 <see langword="true" />；如果没有找到匹配的命名空间节点，或者 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 没有定位在元素节点上，则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="false" />, the position of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="false" />，<see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 的位置将保持不变。

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> has been moved to the namespace node, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A> property reflects the name of the namespace.
trans-unit.target: 后<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>已移动到命名空间节点，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A>属性反映命名空间的名称。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on a namespace node, the methods <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNext%2A>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToPrevious%2A>, and <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFirst%2A> are not applicable.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>位于命名空间节点，方法<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNext%2A>， <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToPrevious%2A>，和<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFirst%2A>不适用。

trans-unit.source: These methods always return `false` and do not change the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 这些方法始终返回`false`，不会更改的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: Rather, you can call <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNextNamespace%2A> to move to the next namespace node.
trans-unit.target: 相反，你可以调用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNextNamespace%2A>可以移到下一步的命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on a namespace node, you can call <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToParent%2A> to move back to the element node.
trans-unit.target: 后<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>位于在命名空间节点上，可以调用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToParent%2A>将移到元素节点。

trans-unit.source: Moves the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> to the next sibling node of the current node.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移至当前节点的下一个同级节点。

trans-unit.source: Moves the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> to the next namespace node.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移动到下一个命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: Moves the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> to the next namespace node.
trans-unit.target: 将 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 移动到下一个命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: Returns <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is successful moving to the next namespace node; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 成功地移动到下一个命名空间节点，则返回 <see langword="true" />；否则返回 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: If <see langword="false" />, the position of the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> is unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果 <see langword="false" />，<see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 的位置将保持不变。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> class returns namespace nodes in reverse document order.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> 类以相反的文档顺序返回命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: Therefore, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNextNamespace%2A> essentially moves to the namespace node above the one in the current scope.
trans-unit.target: 因此，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNextNamespace%2A>实质上移到当前范围内的上一个命名空间节点。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is not currently positioned on a namespace node, this method returns `false` and the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> does not change.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>当前未定位在命名空间节点上，此方法返回`false`和位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>不会更改。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on a namespace node, the methods <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNext%2A>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToPrevious%2A>, and <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFirst%2A> are not applicable.
trans-unit.target: 当<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>位于命名空间节点，方法<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToNext%2A>， <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToPrevious%2A>，和<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToFirst%2A>不适用。

trans-unit.source: These methods always return `false` and do not change the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 这些方法始终返回`false`，不会更改的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: After the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on an namespace node, call <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToParent%2A> to move back to the element node.
trans-unit.target: 后<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>定位在命名空间节点上，调用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.MoveToParent%2A>将移到元素节点。

trans-unit.source: For a definition of namespace nodes, see section 5.4 of the W3C XML Path Language (XPath) recommendation located at http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#data-model.
trans-unit.target: 有关命名空间节点的定义，请参阅 W3C XML 路径语言 (XPath) 建议的 5.4 节位于http://www.w3.org/TR/xpath#data-model。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlNameTable" /> object enabling you to get the atomized version of a <see cref="T:System.String" /> within the XML document.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlNameTable" /> 对象，它使您能够获取 XML 文档中 <see cref="T:System.String" /> 的原子化版本。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XmlNameTable> stores atomized strings of any local name, namespace URI, and prefix used by the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XmlNameTable>存储的任何本地名称、 命名空间 URI 和前缀使用原子化的字符串<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: This means that when the same <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A> is returned multiple times (like "book"), the same <xref:System.String> object is returned for that <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 这意味着，当相同<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A>多次 （例如"book")，返回相同<xref:System.String>对象返回该<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Name%2A>。

trans-unit.source: This makes it possible to write efficient code that does object comparisons on these strings, instead of expensive string comparisons.
trans-unit.target: 这使得可以用来编写高效的代码，未对象比较对这些字符串，而不是昂贵的字符串比较。

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEqualityComparer" /> used for equality comparison of <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 获取 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEqualityComparer" />，它用于 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 对象的相等比较。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEqualityComparer" /> used for equality comparison of <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Collections.IEqualityComparer" />，它用于 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 对象的相等比较。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.NavigatorComparer%2A> property allows <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> objects to be compared on the basis of position rather than reference to the object.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new child element at the beginning of the list of child nodes of the current node using the namespace prefix, local name, and namespace URI specified with the value specified.
trans-unit.target: 使用通过指定值指定的命名空间前缀、本地名称和命名空间 URI 在当前节点的子节点列表的开始处创建一个新的子元素。

trans-unit.source: Prepending a child node adds the new node to the beginning of the list of child nodes for the current node.
trans-unit.target: 预先计算的子节点的操作会将新节点添加到当前节点的子节点列表的开头。

trans-unit.source: For example, when three child nodes exist for an element, the prepended node becomes the first child node.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果的元素有三个子节点，则预置的节点将成为第一个子节点。

trans-unit.source: If no child nodes exist, then a new child node is created.
trans-unit.target: 如果不存在任何子节点，然后创建新的子节点。

trans-unit.source: Namespace prefix and URI values can be obtained by using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupPrefix%2A> or <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupNamespace%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 可以通过获取 Namespace 前缀和 URI 值<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupPrefix%2A>或<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.LookupNamespace%2A>方法。

trans-unit.target: 例如，以下语法将子元素使用的范围内命名空间添加前`xmlns:bk="http://www.contoso.com/books"`:

trans-unit.source: This creates the new child `<bk:pages/>` element.
trans-unit.target: 这将创建新的子`<bk:pages/>`元素。

trans-unit.source: The following are important notes to consider when using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 以下是使用时要考虑的重要说明<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: If the namespace prefix specified is `null` or <xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=nameWithType>, then the prefix for the namespace URI of the new element is obtained from the current namespaces in-scope.
trans-unit.target: 如果指定的命名空间前缀是`null`或<xref:System.String.Empty?displayProperty=nameWithType>，然后从当前命名空间范围内获取的命名空间 URI 的新元素的前缀。

trans-unit.source: If there is no namespace prefix assigned to the specified namespace URI at the current scope, then a namespace prefix is automatically generated.
trans-unit.target: 如果没有分配给指定的命名空间 URI 在当前范围内命名空间前缀，则会自动生成的命名空间前缀。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A> method is valid only when the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on an element node.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A>方法是仅当<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>定位在元素节点上。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A> method does not affect the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.PrependChildElement%2A>方法不会影响的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: Returns an <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> object that contains the current node and its child nodes.
trans-unit.target: 返回 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> 对象，该对象包含当前节点及其子节点。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> object that contains the current node and its child nodes.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlReader" /> 对象，该对象包含当前节点及其子节点。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object is created with the current node and its child nodes, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object's <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadState%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Xml.ReadState.Initial>.
trans-unit.target: 为当前节点及其子节点创建 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 对象时，<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 对象的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadState%2A> 属性设置为 <xref:System.Xml.ReadState.Initial>。

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object's <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Read%2A> method is called for the first time, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> is moved to the current node of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 当首次调用 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 对象的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Read%2A> 方法时，<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 移动到 <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> 的当前节点上。

trans-unit.source: The new <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object continues to read until the end of the XML tree is reached.
trans-unit.target: 新的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 对象继续执行读取操作，直到到达 XML 树的结尾为止。

trans-unit.source: At this point, the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Read%2A> method returns `false` and the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object's <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadState%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Xml.ReadState.EndOfFile>.
trans-unit.target: 此时，<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.Read%2A> 方法返回 `false`，<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> 对象的 <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadState%2A> 属性设置为 <xref:System.Xml.ReadState.EndOfFile>。

trans-unit.source: Changing the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object does not affect the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 更改的位置<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>对象不会影响的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: Namespace declarations for the in-scope namespaces of the current node are not inserted into the XML stream provided to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object.
trans-unit.target: 当前节点的范围内命名空间的 Namespace 声明不会插入到 XML 流提供给<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>对象。

trans-unit.source: This behavior differs from the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 此行为不同于<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: This method creates the <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> object with specific reader settings, and the module that uses this method has no control over those settings.
trans-unit.target: 此方法创建<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>与特定的读取器设置，以及使用此方法的模块的对象具有不能控制这些设置。

trans-unit.source: For example, the reader returned by this method prohibits processing Data Type Definitions (DTDs).
trans-unit.target: 例如，此方法返回的读取器禁止处理数据类型定义 (Dtd)。

trans-unit.source: If the reader attempts to read a file that uses a DTD, it will throw an error, <xref:System.Xml.XmlException>.
trans-unit.target: 如果读取器将尝试读取使用 DTD 的文件，则会引发错误， <xref:System.Xml.XmlException>。

trans-unit.source: The message for the exception will be `Unexpected DTD declaration`.
trans-unit.target: 异常消息将`Unexpected DTD declaration`。

trans-unit.source: You can change this behavior by implementing a custom <xref:System.Xml.XmlResolver> that returns an <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader> with the desired <xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings>.
trans-unit.target: 你可以通过实现自定义更改此行为<xref:System.Xml.XmlResolver>返回<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>与所需<xref:System.Xml.XmlReaderSettings>。

trans-unit.source: Used by <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> implementations which provide a "virtualized" XML view over a store, to provide access to underlying objects.
trans-unit.target: 由在存储区上提供“虚拟化”XML 视图的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator" /> 实现使用，以提供对基础对象的访问。

trans-unit.source: The default is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A> property can be used by <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> implementations which provide a "virtualized" XML view over a store, to provide access to underlying objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A>可以使用属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>实现后者提供了"虚拟化"XML 查看在存储区，以提供对基础对象的访问。

trans-unit.source: For example, if an <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object is used to provide a virtual XML view over a Common Language Runtime (CLR) object graph, you may wish to perform XPath queries using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Select%2A> method and then access the CLR objects underlying the selected nodes.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>对象用于通过公共语言运行时 (CLR) 对象图中提供一个虚拟 XML 视图，你可能想要执行 XPath 查询使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.Select%2A>方法，然后访问所选的节点的 CLR 对象。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A> property would expose these underlying objects.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A>属性将公开这些基础对象。

trans-unit.source: In many cases, this value will be `null`, and the object returned by the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A> property will always be implementation specific.
trans-unit.target: 在许多情况下，此值将为`null`，并返回的对象<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A>属性将始终为特定的实现。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A> property should preserve object identity and should only be used to return objects that have a one-to-one correspondence to their respective overlaid items.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A>属性应保留对象标识，仅应该用于返回到各自的重叠项存在一一对应的关系的对象。

trans-unit.source: A user should always get the same object on successive visits to the same node using the same <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object or a cloned one.
trans-unit.target: 用户应在同一个节点使用相同的连续访问上始终获得相同的对象<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>对象或一个克隆。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A> property of an <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object created by an <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> object returns the corresponding <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.UnderlyingObject%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>创建对象<xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>对象返回相应<xref:System.Xml.XmlNode>。

trans-unit.source: The current node's value as a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> has schema or type information (for example, from an <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> object initialized with an XML schema validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>), and if the current node is defined as an XML Schema `xs:boolean` type, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A> property returns the current node's value as an unboxed <xref:System.Boolean> object.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>具有架构或类型信息 (例如，从<xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>对象使用 XML 架构验证初始化<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>)，如果当前节点指 XML 架构和`xs:boolean`类型，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A>属性返回当前节点的值作为取消装箱<xref:System.Boolean>对象。

trans-unit.source: However, if the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> does not have any schema or type information, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A> property attempts to convert the string value of the current node to a <xref:System.Boolean> value, according to the XPath 2.0 casting rules for `xs:boolean`.
trans-unit.target: 但是，如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>不具有任何架构或类型信息，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A>属性尝试将当前节点为字符串值转换<xref:System.Boolean>值，根据 XPath 2.0 强制转换规则`xs:boolean`。

trans-unit.source: In the following example, the value of each element in the `valueas.xml` file is returned using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsDateTime%2A>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsDouble%2A>, <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsInt%2A>, and <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: 在下面的示例中，在每个元素的值`valueas.xml`文件返回使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A>， <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsDateTime%2A>， <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsDouble%2A>， <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsInt%2A>，和<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The example takes the `valueas.xml` file as an input.

trans-unit.source: The attempted cast to <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> is not valid.
trans-unit.target: 尝试到 <see cref="T:System.Int32" /> 的强制转换无效。

trans-unit.source: Gets the current node's value as an <see cref="T:System.Int64" />.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前节点的 <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 类型的值。

trans-unit.source: The current node's value as an <see cref="T:System.Int64" />.
trans-unit.target: 当前节点的 <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 类型的值。

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> has schema or type information (for example, from an <xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument> object initialized with an XML schema validating <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>), and if the current node is defined as an XML Schema `xs:integer` type, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A> property returns the current node's value as an unboxed <xref:System.Int64> object.
trans-unit.target: 如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>具有架构或类型信息 (例如，从<xref:System.Xml.XmlDocument>对象使用 XML 架构验证初始化<xref:System.Xml.XmlReader>)，如果当前节点指 XML 架构和`xs:integer`类型，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A>属性返回当前节点的值作为取消装箱<xref:System.Int64>对象。

trans-unit.source: However, if the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> does not have any schema or type information, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A> property attempts to convert the string value of the current node to a <xref:System.Int64> value, according to the XPath 2.0 casting rules for `xs:integer`.
trans-unit.target: 但是，如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>不具有任何架构或类型信息，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A>属性尝试将当前节点为字符串值转换<xref:System.Int64>值，根据 XPath 2.0 强制转换规则`xs:integer`。

trans-unit.source: For an example of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A> property, see the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 有关的示例<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsLong%2A>属性，请参阅<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAsBoolean%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The current node's string value cannot be converted to a <see cref="T:System.Int64" />.
trans-unit.target: 当前节点的字符串值不能转换为 <see cref="T:System.Int64" />。

trans-unit.source: The attempted cast to <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> is not valid.
trans-unit.target: 尝试到 <see cref="T:System.Int64" /> 的强制转换无效。

trans-unit.source: Gets the .NET Framework <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the current node.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前节点的 .NET Framework <see cref="T:System.Type" />。

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the current node.
trans-unit.target: 当前节点的 .NET Framework <see cref="T:System.Type" />。

trans-unit.source: The default value is <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: 默认值为 <see cref="T:System.String" />。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A> property gets the .NET Framework <xref:System.Type> of the typed value of the current node.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A>属性获取.NET Framework<xref:System.Type>的当前节点的类型化值。

trans-unit.source: For example, an element of type `xs:int` would have a <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A> of <xref:System.Int32> by default.
trans-unit.target: 例如，类型的元素`xs:int`都<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A>的<xref:System.Int32>默认情况下。

trans-unit.source: However, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A> could be any one of the valid types that can be mapped to `xs:int` such as <xref:System.Int16> or <xref:System.Double>.
trans-unit.target: 但是，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathItem.ValueType%2A>可能是任何一种可以映射到有效类型`xs:int`如<xref:System.Int16>或<xref:System.Double>。

trans-unit.source: If a node has no type, this is equivalent to the type annotation on the node being `xdt:untypedAtomic`.
trans-unit.target: 如果节点没有类型，这相当于节点的类型批注`xdt:untypedAtomic`。

trans-unit.source: In this case, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueType%2A> property returns a string for the node.
trans-unit.target: 在这种情况下，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueType%2A>属性返回节点的字符串。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Type Support in the System.Xml Classes](~/docs/standard/data/xml/type-support-in-the-system-xml-classes.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[System.Xml 类中的类型支持](~/docs/standard/data/xml/type-support-in-the-system-xml-classes.md)。

trans-unit.source: In the following example, the `contosoBooks.xml` XML file and `contosoBooks.xsd` XML Schema definition language (XSD) schema are used to create an <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> object.
trans-unit.target: 在下面的示例中， `contosoBooks.xml` XML 文件和`contosoBooks.xsd`XML 架构定义语言 (XSD) 架构用于创建<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>对象。

trans-unit.source: The typed value of the `price` element is displayed using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueType%2A> property and then returned as a string using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAs%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 类型化的值`price`元素将显示使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueType%2A>属性，然后返回为字符串使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.ValueAs%2A>方法。

trans-unit.source: The example takes the `contosoBooks.xml` file as an input.
trans-unit.target: 该示例使用 `contosoBooks.xml` 文件作为输入。

trans-unit.source: The example also takes the `contosoBooks.xsd` as an input.
trans-unit.target: 该示例还使用 `contosoBooks.xsd` 作为输入。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> object to stream to.
trans-unit.target: 要流式传输至的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Streams the current node and its child nodes to the <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> object specified.
trans-unit.target: 将当前节点及其子节点流式传输到指定的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> 对象。

trans-unit.source: Namespace declarations for the in-scope namespaces of the current node are inserted into the XML streamed to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> object specified.
trans-unit.target: 当前节点的范围内命名空间的 Namespace 声明插入到流式传输到的 XML<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>指定对象。

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A> method is called on the first `book` element of the `books.xml` file, the `http://www.contoso.com/books` namespace declaration made at the top of the XML document will appear in the XML streamed to the <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter> object specified as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A>调用方法的第一天`book`元素`books.xml`文件，`http://www.contoso.com/books`在 XML 文档的顶部所做的命名空间声明将出现在流式传输到的 XML 中<xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>指定的对象下面的示例中所示。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A> method does not affect the position of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A>方法不会影响的位置<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。

trans-unit.source: The following example illustrates using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A> method on the first `book` element of the `contosoBooks.xml` file.
trans-unit.target: 下面的示例演示如何使用<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.WriteSubtree%2A>方法的第一天`book`元素`contosoBooks.xml`文件。

trans-unit.source: The example takes the `contosoBooks.xml` file as an input.
trans-unit.target: 该示例使用 `contosoBooks.xml` 文件作为输入。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <c>xml:lang</c> scope for the current node.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前节点的 <c>xml:lang</c> 范围。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the value of the <c>xml:lang</c> scope, or <see cref="F:System.String.Empty" /> if the current node has no <c>xml:lang</c> scope value to return.
trans-unit.target: A<see cref="T:System.String" />包含值的<c>xml: lang</c>作用域，或<see cref="F:System.String.Empty" />如果当前节点没有<c>xml: lang</c>确定要返回的值的范围。

trans-unit.source: In the example XML below, when the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is positioned on the `name` element, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlLang%2A> property returns a scope of `en-us` indicating that the node is in the scope of a `xml:lang="en-us"` attribute.
trans-unit.target: 在示例中，XML 时<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>位于`name`元素，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlLang%2A>属性返回的作用域`en-us`指示节点是否在范围内`xml:lang="en-us"`属性。

trans-unit.source: Gets the <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaType" /> information for the current node.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前节点的 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaType" /> 信息。

trans-unit.source: An <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaType" /> object; default is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaType" /> 对象；默认值为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The following are important notes to consider when using the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: 以下是使用时要考虑的重要说明<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A>属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A> property is `null`, unless the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.Validity%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator> is set to <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaValidity.Valid?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A>属性是`null`，除非<xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.Validity%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>设置为<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchemaValidity.Valid?displayProperty=nameWithType>。

trans-unit.source: If this node is valid, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A> property is the same as the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>, unless this node is a member of a union.
trans-unit.target: 此节点是否有效，<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A>属性等同于<xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.SchemaType%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>，除非此节点是联合的成员。

trans-unit.source: If this node is a member of a union, the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A> property is the same as the <xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.MemberType%2A> property of the <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A> property of this <xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>.
trans-unit.target: 如果此节点是一个联合成员<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.XmlType%2A>属性等同于<xref:System.Xml.Schema.IXmlSchemaInfo.MemberType%2A>属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator.SchemaInfo%2A>此属性<xref:System.Xml.XPath.XPathNavigator>。
